5 Subject: Municipal and county government; Vermont Municipal Response and
6 Recovery Special Fund
7 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to create the
8 Vermont Municipal Response and Recovery Special Fund to provide direct
9 assistance to municipalities for flood response, prevention, and resiliency
10 projects. This act also proposes to require the State Treasurer to report to the
11 General Assembly on or before December 1, 2025 concerning
12 recommendations for the distribution of monies from the Fund and any
13 potential amendments to current programs that would enable flood-impacted
14 communities to have priority access to State assistance.
15 An act relating to creating the Vermont Municipal Response and Recovery
16 Special Fund
17 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
18 Sec. 1. 20 V.S.A § 49a is added to read:
19 § 49a. VERMONT MUNICIPAL RESPONSE AND RECOVERY SPECIAL
20 FUND
